{"tid":1719844,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府>黑警>鄉黑>藍絲, 政府執雞","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:25:27.000Z","uid":64810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"656756ad2658082459c4b64846dda9728098b626","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"我分幾點講想睇重點嘅就睇紅字<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">咪作假新聞 相信前線手足</span><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">掃走主面上既左報 減少洗腦 特別東方</span> 要教育佢地唔好人講就信 我知好難 但依家係假新聞最多既階段<br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重欠缺文文宣 出師無名 要將社會現象歸咎政府</span> ：琴日曉打講既 政府若果好 社會就唔會咁 、運動已經持續左五個啦 政府完全無誠意解決問題 縱容警暴導致 切記我地都要拉一派打一派 政府拉緊港豬入藍 我地唔止要拉攏返佢地變黃 仲要拉埋內地人落如果做到既話<br />\n<br />\n4<span style=\"color: red;\">海外報導開始唔幫示威者 </span>我地要加強海外文宣 / Twitter<br />\n<br />\n5<span style=\"color: red;\">形象塑造要加強 近日實在太撚多暴力畫面 中共喉舌有大量彈藥</span>（唔該你地記得black boc..) 我地需要有和平既集會/咩都好 去挽回自己嘅形象呢點好撚重要 美國副總統已經講到明。經過4日既黎明行動 我地好撚成功但美圖白宮對CU單嘢無出過聲 我唔知係中美貿易定點 定係我地既形象既問題 但切記我地都需要和善既形象<br />\n今晚有支持消防員既集會 去唔到愛丁堡既人 不如喺同一時間係自己區內搞集會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾鬥民眾最恐怖係 你放棄形象為左藍屍而犧牲. 黑警會鎮壓平息而中共唔洗再出老解</span>"},{"pid":"3bb267d15e925d22d4bdcb3d35ba2cd522ad22c0","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09a7198926a4b8638e9ea197235b52cb98a702f","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a886c6dacbdfe80c78d334b033397af2b99341","tid":1719844,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"冇DDOS都知乜嘢事㗎啦<br />\n好多五毛入嚟煽動大毆鬥！各位記住敵進我退，由得佢哋鳩企！遲啲先搵佢哋啲鋪頭找數"},{"pid":"db33e657e0c5b4e4d3751804bc51b7e8d2fd25fe","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c173c8a80f59fb51552c535cbad76354cb4ad3b0","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53226ef33178b57d9dcd6b2cc8ffd5fbbea25ed","tid":1719844,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b9d37107da7052d318cc05d10e16ea50e565c9a2","tid":1719844,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a44c9f06d6793033bf726b8edbee0ea1e09e71","tid":1719844,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"鄭立：大學係「要塞」 唔係防守而係攻擊據點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718775</a>"}]}